Extract from the minutes of the 42nd meeting of managers of the Kiev branch of the laboratory 15 from 09.09.96\nPresent: 

Director of the Research Laboratories Network - S.K. Frankevich.
Head of Kiev branch of laboratory No. 15 - I.L. Karteevich.
Deputy Head of Kiev Branch of Laboratory No.15 - Ah.G. Lavrikov.

Decided: to recognize the further performance of the Kiev branch of the laboratory  15 incapable. Grounds: lack of funding, partial leakage of information on the laboratory's developments, threat to the existence of other secret facilities, distrust of the staff.

Next Steps:
- Laboratory personnel shall immediately make copies of laboratory reports. Destroy the original classified documents;
- to transfer all available documents to Prof. Chubko K.P;
- all personnel, starting from the head of the Kiev branch and ending with laboratory technicians and cleaners, to undergo procedure B, in order to further preserve the secrecy of developments. Perform the procedure at low power (~100 Jigowatts);
- in the event that any of the personnel resists, action must be taken;
- monitor the mental state of staff for 3 months after the B procedure;
- on the results of procedure B to Prof. Chubko K.P.

Secretary of the meeting

Lavrentiev Ah.L.
